classGroups.filter: SchoolYear = @SchoolYear AND ParentClassID IS NULL AND IsNotPresentForm=0

classGroupNotPresent.filter: SchoolYear = @SchoolYear AND ParentClassID IS NULL AND IsNotPresentForm=1

curriculums.filter: SchoolYear = @SchoolYear AND Curriculum.SubjectTypeID NOT IN (152,153,154,155,156) AND ParentCurriculumID IS NULL AND IsValid=1

subCurriculums.filter: SchoolYear = @SchoolYear AND ParentCurriculumID IS NOT NULL AND IsValid=1

person.filter: PersonID IN (SELECT PersonID FROM core.EducationalState WHERE InstitutionID = @InstitutionID)
